{"tid":304124,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"LIHKG環球女神冠軍盃台灣區分組賽名額附加賽－田馥甄vs楊丞琳","createTime":"2017-06-30T16:00:01.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-01T19:46:01.000Z","uid":92376,"like":107,"dislike":134,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8d7aec38065e2712ab4d947a375ffb9b1b2a415b","tid":304124,"uid":92376,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T16:00:01.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">LIHKG環球女神冠軍盃台灣區分組賽名額附加賽</div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">2017-7-1 12am-10pm</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/vEiMk9Z.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FvEiMk9Z.png&h=9be2f60e&s={SIZE}\" />  <img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/Z1EdpLG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FZ1EdpLG.png&h=6410f6bd&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">田馥甄 vs 楊丞琳</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">賽事時限為22小時，會員可於本帖發起後22小時內於以正負評方式(前者正評;後者負評)投選心水賽事女神。<br />\n在<span style=\"color: red;\">指定時段外</span>的正負評投票<span style=\"color: red;\">將不作計算</span>在內，請會員密切留意比賽時間。</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">附加賽不設額外分數，會員請踴躍投票支持參賽者。</div>"},{"pid":"31b3a315f2c86724e040f2f12396d4caf4626902","tid":304124,"uid":2313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T16:00:31.000Z","msg":"丞琳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0c2e180a418275984f7a8af608293a044d78c5d","tid":304124,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T16:03:27.000Z","msg":"呢個賽事將會決定台灣最後一個直接出線今季環冠盃分組賽既資格,贏既有位,輸既會參加附加賽,根據早兩日既抽籤,台灣代表將會喺最後階段既附加賽對香港聯賽第4名-陳穎欣@SG<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cdce77907da666e53049e65dcac9a509d08b1929","tid":304124,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T16:07:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0141ffb9b5d4dc1b99cba948b40cc6dccf29e1eb","tid":304124,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T16:11:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>丞琳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n多謝你踴躍支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90ce4dc0fba05a678d9241095f02e5d985c0f90d","tid":304124,"uid":27970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T16:12:43.000Z","msg":"丞琳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4ff3845d51a753656b45235994ba8f67a26a0ab","tid":304124,"uid":27970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T16:13:39.000Z","msg":"13分鐘，有15票<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd25d4224001f136273deaa794354a865dac784d","tid":304124,"uid":27970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T16:14:23.000Z","msg":"恭喜樓主，我估百幾二百票不是夢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7e02b5dfe0d91bb70343db719b6607401dc21cb","tid":304124,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T16:15:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>13分鐘，有15票<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n正負評係好少少咁啦,但多賽事黎講要撳入黎先知有咩賽事就怕啲人唔想入黎睇下邊個對邊個搞到又會少左人投,有回覆評分功能都無乜用<br />\n但如果真係咁既話我都無辦法啦,連入黎睇睇,再撳幾下掣投左佢都唔想既話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b3010be82f3fd6c1474d02c2f34a70