ore":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T16:23:21.000Z","msg":"22分鐘，20票<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4b30ebf506d29c2c6ea7a8c0d4babc6f7c3eeb0","tid":304124,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T16:26:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>恭喜樓主，我估百幾二百票不是夢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n如果下周亞洲挑戰盃試用回覆評分功能都有咁多人投就好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有乜唔同？</blockquote><br />\n依家係正負評,喺topic已經知係hebe對rainie<br />\n但喺多場賽事一齊喺同一個post舉行既情況之下,我地要撳入去先知有咩賽事<br />\n咁到時我地會用到回覆評分功能,即係每個回覆既左下會出現既上箭咀同下箭咀<br />\n<br />\n我下星期六會12:28分開post,然後分別喺30分同32分,以回覆既形式開以下兩組賽事,你地就可以用回覆評分功能去投票<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">LIHKG香港超級女神聯賽亞洲挑戰盃中國站</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">初賽日</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">2017-7-8 12:30am-10:30pm</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/7TCJwS8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F7TCJwS8.png&h=93e97456&s={SIZE}\" />  <img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/clu1GSf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fclu1GSf.png&h=fe7c2b0d&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/A9BLxCB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FA9BLxCB.png&h=dbd0240d&s={SIZE}\" />李一桐vs李靜儀@SG</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">賽事時限為22小時，會員可於本回覆發起後22小時內於以回覆評分功能(前者上箭咀;後者下箭咀)投選心水賽事女神。<br />\n在<span style=\"color: red;\">指定時段外</span>的回覆評分功能投票<span style=\"color: red;\">將不作計算</span>在內，請會員密切留意比賽時間。</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">友誼賽不設額外分數，會員請踴躍投票支持參賽者。</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">初賽日</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">2017-7-8 12:32am-10:32pm</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/90BwhA3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F90BwhA3.png&h=e79a77ae&s={SIZE}\" />  <img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/reyTtq5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FreyTtq5.png&h=52b7ec3f&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">馮盈盈vs倪晨曦</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">賽事時限為22小時，會員可於本回覆發起後22小時內於以回覆評分功能(前者上箭咀;後者下箭咀)投選心水賽事女神。<br />\n在<span style=\"color: red;\">指定時段外</span>的回覆評分功能投票<span style=\"color: red;\">將不作計算</span>在內，請會員密切留意比賽時間。</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">友誼賽不設額外分數，會員請踴躍投票支持參賽者。</div>"},{"pid":"039cd92d321f9f8abcd572cd5fda55950d9b01c2","tid":304124,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T16:28:56.000Z","msg":"既然都喺上面貼左少少,都順便講多少少,除左陳寶珊呢個虛構人物我換唔到相之外,下季各級聯賽我都會換新相<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">唔保證所有人滿意,我盡量揀出公平,以不過份美化不過份醜化作準則既149x149像素圖黎作為佢地下季既參賽圖片</span></span>"},{"pid":"1e98e4cd8715f3a865609e336bf31fce9a891b44","tid":304124,"uid":27970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T16:29:03.000Z","msg":"我覺得最好應該係呢個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19466638ad224e73e58f3e5c3d6e3c8f10a6232a","tid":304124,"uid":27970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T16:29:26.000Z","msg":"29分鐘，22票<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ece31