/>\n游蕙禎vs駱文捷<br />\n朱晨麗vs李嘉欣<br />\n余香凝vs周慧敏<br />\n梁嘉琪vs李施嬅<br />\n黃智雯vs蓋世寶<br />\n蘇麗珊vs陳婉婷<br />\n胡琳vs陳潔玲<br />\n劉穎鏇vs鍾楚紅<br />\n何雁詩vs勞嘉怡<br />\n<br />\n不過上季我係貼晒之後啲對賽,最後先貼返張list,但今季我就會喺開post時講左先,咁睇下會點樣啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd96c4df39f2d864b63864d626526e4511ebb1a5","tid":304124,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T16:33:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我覺得最好應該係呢個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n起碼多人直接睇到同會直接投票</blockquote><br />\n你睇下我上面#21,現實黎講難啲做到"},{"pid":"625d213df0d9be1197cc56f351f4c357e1dbca19","tid":304124,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T16:36:02.000Z","msg":"不過老實講,以2分鐘開始一場黎講,最慘就實係果一輪較後開始比賽果幾位<br />\n一黎人地早左出發,二黎佢地果場要拉落啲先見到,變相佢地有機會最少人投<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2daaf7f18f3b53a611be9b8e7572c64def484079","tid":304124,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T16:40:26.000Z","msg":"但都係果句,現階段已經爭取到<br />\n1.唔駛回覆逐個人名填<br />\n2.唔駛比人知自己有份投同投左<br />\n3.只係撳幾個掣(回覆評分功能)<br />\n做到咁樣,投票既人只係需要入去個post望一望有咩賽事,然後再逐場撳掣投,如果咁既地步都覺得好為難,咁我都無計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db789e77fb09d94939974ed10da0bb0566ac203f","tid":304124,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T16:40:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>但都係果句,現階段已經爭取到<br />\n1.唔駛回覆逐個人名填<br />\n2.唔駛比人知自己有份投同投左啲咩<br />\n3.只係撳幾個掣(回覆評分功能)<br />\n做到咁樣,投票既人只係需要入去個post望一望有咩賽事,然後再逐場撳掣投,如果咁既地步都覺得好為難,咁我都無計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"5f36aba6186659ecb6b950403673c1dd6942f171","tid":304124,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T16:42:08.000Z","msg":"hebe啲後勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c3889178b2fa48566f39c8cf9ab0e839542b8ba","tid":304124,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T16:44:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b216e2a20ee07257a92a6f0c8cd4d326b23e21f5","tid":304124,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T16:49:31.000Z","msg":"49分鐘有35票,還不錯"},{"pid":"74a3d290ab120f02c373217bc9808529b16286cd","tid":304124,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T16:51:30.000Z","msg":"不過最近10分鐘楊丞琳又拉返開"},{"pid":"a50ba0b225f09a4b7afff6d4bc1f7549fcb5549e","tid":304124,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T16:55:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5feaf1398efc12db1c4dc786fea29afa01c17c8f","tid":304124,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T16:59:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bda8cdf073e1a2874d483d5963206442cc5541fb","tid":304124,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T17:01:22.000Z","msg":"唔推住啦,個post得我推係上唔到去,等人接力算了"},{"pid":"d577ec3de0e6be9b41f5fa4afb9f5c36a852088d","tid":304124,"uid":53909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T17:15:43.000Z","msg":"Rainie <img src=\"/assets/faces/n