mg src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f8988d062d1f6275cd544feee21e5136df09a57","tid":304124,"uid":27970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T05:09:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我覺得最好應該係呢個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n但無計,你唔通想我每2分鐘開一個新post然後洗晒版比人屌柒咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n如果分開一日2-3場對賽開post，有冇得諗？"},{"pid":"4b866a0091349b93457533e55b99171f430a20d8","tid":304124,"uid":27970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T05:11:11.000Z","msg":"贏咁少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f24280024d5004147f7f6f312314490820187ad7","tid":304124,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T05:13:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我覺得最好應該係呢個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n但無計,你唔通想我每2分鐘開一個新post然後洗晒版比人屌柒咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n如果分開一日2-3場對賽開post，有冇得諗？</blockquote><br />\n咁我真係全年無休啦喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n再講,其實我係想比其他人搞other區域既聯賽,就算依家未有<br />\n但我都應該要鬆返個空間出黎<br />\n同埋個人黎講唔太建議閒日都開,閒日開足22個鐘同weekend比係好大分別<br />\nBTW我打算係 超聯1post8場 冠聯1post9場 甲 乙都係各1post 9場<br />\n我諗呢個已經係盡量降低影響既方法<br />\n唔好睇連登流量咁高,我覺得娛樂台係少人開post,如果一戰一post隨時重演膠登既結局<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df8ccd60e0b51b059a54797f1c7abd40aafb824b","tid":304124,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T05:16:47.000Z","msg":"同埋大家要自律,我用回覆既形式以每2mins既速度開賽事,計冠甲乙,我係需要18分鐘先開得晒,期間大家唔好reply住,等賽事開晒先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f90e91d6e8d586385cb879dc1955506f1bab93fe","tid":304124,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T05:20:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00f9f62da488e92291f481cf99a10b372861ed27","tid":304124,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T05:26:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24d95554c4a7928e679096fe1423f654148ec31f","tid":304124,"uid":83759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T05:28:57.000Z","msg":"投左楊丞琳 細個睇惡魔在身邊 愛上左佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3784ec78904be9a75c72107ffc1ac960ff6c649","tid":304124,"uid":25857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T05:33:47.000Z","msg":"Hebe<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"377aaf54beb2325b05b29a928f3e572b33da7cef","tid":304124,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T05:35:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>投左楊丞琳 細個睇惡魔在身邊 愛上左佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n多謝你投票支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2ea58b510cc05c7a28638b24ddb17cbd88117e7","tid":304124,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T05:35:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Hebe<img src=\"/assets/faces/norm